            "Sound": "SE_Cartoon_01",
            "Transition": 0,
            "BGName": 0,
            "BGEffect": 0,
            "PopupFileName": "",
            "ScriptKr": "3;미치루;04;앗-뜨, 거엇! 뭐, 뭐야?! 우, 우와아앗?!\n#3;stiff",
            "TextJp": "あっっっつ！？なになに！？熱いんだけど！？",
            "VoiceId": 0
